Normal Operation (with OIFITS)

./oifits-sim -t ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/target_epsAur.txt  -s ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC_LowH.txt  -d ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/2008Dec10-eps_Aur.oifits  -i ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC.txt   -a ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/CHARA.txt  -o /tmp/test.oifits

Debugging:

gdb ./oifits-sim
run -t ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/target_epsAur.txt  -s ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC_LowH.txt  -d ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/2008Dec10-eps_Aur.oifits  -i ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/MIRC.txt   -a ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/CHARA.txt  -o /tmp/test.oifits


Normal Operation (with txt)

./oifits-sim -t ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/Target_EpsAur.txt -s ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/SpectralMode_MIRC_LowH.txt -h ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/HA-Night1.txt -i ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/Instrument_MIRC.txt  -a ~/Projects/CHARA/simulator_info/CHARA_S1E1W1W2.txt -o /tmp/test2.oifits
